To install the kernel code, from the directory containing the 'ds' directory:

cp -r ds $INFERNOROOT/os
cp $INFERNOROOT/os/ds/dsinit.b $INFERNOROOT/os/init
cd $INFERNOROOT/os/ds; mk

also inferno for the ds requires the devkitpro utilities ndstool(to build a .nds file usuable with normal ds flashcards) and dsbuild(for making .nds.gba kernel files, loadable using a gba flashcard and a passme). Devkitpro is available from http://www.devkitpro.org/.

Please note that this code does not use any nintendo intellectual property.

